Revision history for Logwatch::RecordTree

2.056     2015-06-02 11:26:19-07:00 America/Los_Angeles
    Add Net::IP::Identifier => 0.111 to prerequisites (for Testers)

2.055     2015-06-01 11:23:45-07:00 America/Los_Angeles
    Add VERSION in IPv4.pm

    Move 'use' line defaults capability from IPv4 to base class
        (RecordTree).  IPv4 no longer automatically sets the neat_names
        flag (set it in the 'use' line instead - see scripts for examples).

    Update example scripts to set neat_names for IPv4, and to 'use aliased'
        IPv4 for make them more readable.  Some other minor script
        improvements.

    Fix problem in Net::IP::Identifier that caused multiple CPAN Tester
        failures, and require fixed Identifier version (or later) in IPv4.


2.046    2015-04-10
    Original release.

